At Mydressfinder.com, our aim is simple – provide all over latest stylish fashionable wardrobe directory. It will include guides about latest trends and styles to who cater all of your fashion needs – keeping it practical and easy to apply. That is why, we are UAE's first and finest teenage magazine dedicated to fun, humor, fashion, horoscopes, latest trends, advertisement free and ideals for girls.

Cindy (Editor)

I am originally from Syria where I guess fashion was my passion even at my young age. When I moved to Dubai I aspired to study Fashion Design and Fashion Management, but due to personal reasons I had to re-direct my path. I have been working in the fashion retail sector for just one and a half year as a store manager. I like fashion because every way is a way to express your creativity and your feelings!!!!!

Karima (Creative Manager)

I am 20 years old, originally from Egypt but in Dubai for 18 years now. I'm studying Strategic Communications at American University in Dubai. I have always been very creative I liked to draw & write when I was a kid, and then discovered I had other creative outlets as well like doing my hair & make-up, that is why I decided to make a career out of it.

I also write creative articles on different fashion websites to gain experience, some of them include – Pops
